<font color="#FF0000">SORRY/HISTORY LESSONS</font><br>
<tt>Thu Feb  6  0:59:06 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Well, first off, my apologies to Mike Toliver and, especially, Doc Del, whose eloquent posts are always welcome. It's nice too see that most folks who post here are tolerant of other's views, even if not in agreement. I certainly have NO ill feelings toward any vet, and am sorry if any of you have read that &quot;into&quot; my posts.  I just get a little carried away sometimes, most often when somebody &quot;reads stuff into&quot; what I've said.  ******Some things that amaze me as I've read 100's of these posts are how s-o-m-e vets *still* (1) blame protesters for our &quot;defeat,&quot; (2) don't know much about History, (3) despise those of us who didn't serve.******I would like to offer a sincere thanks to Tanker for the History lesson, mainly because you saved me a lot of typing.  But you got a lot of the history kinda mixed up.  Panama- no business there.  Grenada- a fuckin' joke.  Sp/Amer War- naked imperialism.  European countries had overseas possesions, we didn't.  Spain was weak.  We go to war and take their possessions. Wave them flags!******Hats off to Jeffrey Winkler for correcting Tanker's errors. You must be a History teacher******And don't forget Nicaragua!  We invaded in 1928, left in 1933 after installing Somoza in power.  47 years later the chickens came home to roost.*****El Salvador.  50,000 peasants killed in the 1930's.  14 families own everything.  In the 70's the peasants, tired of being exploited, rise up.  14 families call the peasants commies.  Uncle Sam rushes in.  50,000 die.  Nobody cares.*****Chile.  Yeah, we didn't pull the triggers, we just supplied the guns and training.  Any demonstrations against Allende were sponsored by the CIA, ITT, etc.  Read your History books!  Chile W-A-S the only country in LAmer to have been a democracy since it's birth. The U.S. ended that streak!******Guatemala. Read &quot;Bitter Fruit.&quot;  I have.  The only democratically elected President in their history says he's gonna nationalize (and pay for) some of the land owned by the United Fruit Company which, at the time, only owned 80% of the land worth owning in Guatemala and farmed (bananas) on but 10% of that.  So all of a sudden he's labled a communist and the CIA gets rid of him. And G's been fucked up ever since.******Look, there are reasons why some people in some countries don't like us much.  Instead of hating them back it MIGHT be in our interests to find out *why* they hate us. Maybe they have good reasons.  Iran is a good example.*****Sorry for the long post.  Later guys.<br>
Nurse Ratchet
